@node __dpmi_get_memory_information, dpmi
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <dpmi.h>

int __dpmi_get_memory_information(__dpmi_memory_info *_buffer);
@end example

@subheading Description

Please refer to @ref{DPMI Specification} for details on DPMI
function call operation.  Also see @ref{DPMI Overview} for general
information.

DPMI function AX = 0x050b (DPMI 1.0 only)

This function returns virtual memory information.

@subheading Return Value

-1 on error, else zero.
